(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/de/models/2693321', 'Dandelion Flower Series - HueForge Wall Art', 58, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€125/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-25T19:23:05.696Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/de/models/2693321","source_host":"makerworld.com/de/models/2693321","score":"58","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Dandelion Flower Series - HueForge Wall Art","description":"A multi-filament HueForge wall art piece depicting a dandelion mid-release, printed in four tonal layers (Black, Blue Gray, Gray, White) at 0.08mm for fine photographic detail. Designed as a calm, airy décor print suitable for gifting or home display.","author":"novy","print_time_ai":"4.4h","material_ai":"~45g PLA (4-colour HueForge swap)","downloads":"","likes":"","search_volume":"9500","search_trend":"→ Stable","etsy_listings":"12000","etsy_avg_price":"€14","market_insight":"<b>Wall art on Etsy has strong evergreen demand</b>, but the category is saturated with digital prints and posters selling at €2–8, making physical 3D-printed pieces harder to justify without a clear differentiation story. <b>HueForge specifically is a niche within a niche</b> — buyers who understand the process perceive it as premium and handcrafted, but the majority of Etsy shoppers have never heard of HueForge, so the listing must explain the technique visually. <b>Dandelion motifs trend seasonally</b> around spring and Mother''s Day (March–May), which offers a short but meaningful revenue window that a new seller should plan for with listings live at least 6 weeks before peak.","sell_price":"€10.00","units_per_month":"18","gross_revenue":"180","print_cost":"32","etsy_fees":"23","net_profit":"125","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":"Tonal layering — HueForge''s colour-depth effect is physically impossible to replicate with laser cutting, offset printing, or injection moulding, giving the finished piece a genuinely unique handcrafted identity that buyers cannot source elsewhere at this price point.","etsy_ban_risk":"medium","etsy_ban_reason":"The scraped listing states that ''commercial rights to sell physical prints are available through a paid Patreon membership'' — this means a commercial license exists but must be actively purchased from the designer (novy","legal_risk":"","legal_desc":"","copyright_risk":"","copyright_desc":"","best_platform":"","category":"decor","marketplace":"etsy","price_range":"5-15","print_time_input":"","material_input":"","seller_goal":"side-hustle","printer_count":"","printer_type":"","experience":"new","weekly_time":"","active_markets":"","social_media":"","sell_from":"","sell_to":"WORLDWIDE","legal_flags":"none"}}'::jsonb, NULL, '2026-04-25T19:23:05.696Z'),
