(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/de/models/2693321', 'Dandelion Flower Series – HueForge Wall Art Print', 52, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€257/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-25T20:20:16.468Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/de/models/2693321","source_host":"makerworld.com/de/models/2693321","score":"52","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Dandelion Flower Series – HueForge Wall Art Print","description":"A multi-filament HueForge wall art piece depicting a dandelion at the moment of seed release, printed in four tonal layers across Black, Blue Gray, Gray, and White PLA. Designed for clean tonal separation and beginner-friendly printing despite its fine structural detail.","author":"novy","print_time_ai":"4.4h","material_ai":"~55g PLA (4-colour filament swap, estimated across 28 layers at 0.08mm, 100% infill, 1 wall)","downloads":"","likes":"","search_volume":"9400","search_trend":"→ Stable","etsy_listings":"12000","etsy_avg_price":"€22","market_insight":"<b>Demand for botanical and nature-themed wall art is steady on Etsy, but competition is extremely high</b> — digital printables, canvas prints, and laser-engraved wood pieces undercut 3D-printed wall art on both price and perceived finish quality at this tier. <b>HueForge prints occupy a small but genuine niche</b>: buyers who specifically seek out layered-filament art do exist, but they are a small fraction of general wall art traffic and require education in the listing about what HueForge actually is. Production at 4.4h per unit on a single unspecified FDM printer allows roughly 3 units per day maximum — manageable for a testing phase but a bottleneck if demand spikes.","sell_price":"€22.00","units_per_month":"18","gross_revenue":"396","print_cost":"39","etsy_fees":"100","net_profit":"257","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":"Tonal depth — the HueForge filament-swap tech