(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/de/models/2693321', 'Dandelion Flower Series – HueForge Wall Art', 52, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€222/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-25T20:23:19.077Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/de/models/2693321","source_host":"makerworld.com/de/models/2693321","score":"52","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Dandelion Flower Series – HueForge Wall Art","description":"A multi-filament HueForge wall art print depicting a dandelion in the moment of seed release, using four tonal layers (black, blue-gray, gray, white) to create soft contrast and movement. Designed specifically for FDM tonal printing, it is beginner-friendly despite its fine detail.","author":"novy","print_time_ai":"4.4h","material_ai":"Estimated 60–80g PLA (4 colours, 100% infill, 0.08mm layers)","downloads":"","likes":"","search_volume":"9400","search_trend":"↑ 12% YoY","etsy_listings":"18000","etsy_avg_price":"€22","market_insight":"<b>Botanical and nature wall art is a crowded but proven Etsy category</b> — demand peaks strongly in November–December and around Mother''s Day, giving a clear seasonal window for a new seller to gain early reviews. <b>HueForge as a format is a meaningful differentiator</b> because the tonal filament-layer technique is visually distinctive from standard flat prints or paper prints, and buyers who encounter it often remark on the craft story. However, with 18,000+ wall art listings on Etsy, a new seller without reviews will struggle for organic visibility without a strong SEO strategy and competitive photography — <b>colour personalisation (offering different background palettes) is the single most accessible way to stand out</b> at this price point.","sell_price":"€11.00","units_per_month":"30","gross_revenue":"330","print_cost":"62","etsy_fees":"46","net_profit":"222","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":