(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/models/571733?appSharePlatform=copy', '#0001 - Bulbasaur Ball', 22, 'Don''t sell — Pokémon IP blocker', NULL, '~€299/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-27T05:28:35.787Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/models/571733?appSharePlatform=copy","source_host":"makerworld.com/models/571733","score":"22","verdict":"Don''t sell — Pokémon IP blocker","title":"#0001 - Bulbasaur Ball","description":"A multi-colour decorative ball featuring Bulbasaur from the Pokémon franchise, designed for AMS or split-plate FDM printing in up to five filament colours. The model is actively maintained with design updates and is optimised for Bambu Lab printers.","author":"N3D","print_time_ai":"4h 18m","material_ai":"~65g PLA (multi-colour, estimated across all components)","downloads":"","likes":"9400","search_volume":"28000","search_trend":"↑ 18% YoY","etsy_listings":"14000","etsy_avg_price":"€19","market_insight":"<b>Demand for Pokémon-themed novelty items is among the highest in the gaming/gift category on Etsy</b>, with strong evergreen interest and seasonal spikes around game releases and holiday gifting. However, <b>over 14,000 competing listings exist</b> and Etsy''s IP enforcement team regularly sweeps this category — shops without a licence from The Pokémon Company face sudden listing removal and account suspension. Buyer perception of 3D-printed Pokémon figures is positive in the hobbyist community, but retail buyers compare these to mass-produced official merchandise and expect low prices, compressing margins. <b>Production is manageable on a single printer</b> at roughly 3 units per day, but fulfilment overhead for worldwide shipping will erode net profit significantly.","sell_price":"€19.00","units_per_month":"20","gross_revenue":"380","print_cost":"43","etsy_fees":"38","net_profit":"299","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":"Zero tooling — the