(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/models/2165336?appSharePlatform=copy', 'Rectangular Twisted Lamp with Basket Structure', 52, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€357/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-27T05:56:21.726Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/models/2165336?appSharePlatform=copy","source_host":"makerworld.com/models/2165336","score":"52","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Rectangular Twisted Lamp with Basket Structure","description":"A modular 3D-printed rectangular twisted lampshade featuring a bayonet-lock base system compatible with E27 fittings, IKEA Strala, and Bambu Lamp Kit 001. Designed by Super_Laserkatz as part of a swappable lamp ecosystem.","author":"Super_Laserkatz","print_time_ai":"15.6h","material_ai":"Estimated 280–350g PLA","downloads":"","likes":"","search_volume":"9400","search_trend":"→ Stable","etsy_listings":"4200","etsy_avg_price":"€22","market_insight":"<b>Decorative lamp demand on Etsy is stable year-round with a gifting spike in November–December</b>, but the market is dominated by sellers with established shop trust and polished brand presentation. Buyers searching for 3D-printed lamps are a small, design-savvy niche — they value uniqueness but expect a finished, professional-looking product, meaning visible FDM layer lines can undermine perceived value unless addressed with sanding, painting, or transparent/silk filament. <b>Production is a hard constraint</b>: at 15.6h per unit on a single printer, a new seller can realistically complete only 1 unit per day, capping monthly output at roughly 20–25 units before accounting for failures and fulfilment time — making scaling extremely slow without additional printers.","sell_price":"€84.00","units_per_month":"8","gross_revenue":"672","print_cost":"231","etsy_fees":"84","net_profit":"357","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":"Geometry — the twisted baske