(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/sv/models/2320985-large-illuminated-lunar-wall-lamp-version-2#profileId-2534929', 'Large Illuminated Lunar Wall Lamp - Version 2', 62, 'Good for the right audience', NULL, '~€162/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:29:19.105Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/sv/models/2320985-large-illuminated-lunar-wall-lamp-version-2#profileId-2534929","source_host":"makerworld.com/sv/models/2320985-large-illuminated-lunar-wall-lamp-version-2","score":"62","verdict":"Good for the right audience","title":"Large Illuminated Lunar Wall Lamp - Version 2","description":"A high-detail 50 cm illuminated Moon wall lamp based on real lunar surface data, featuring realistic surface relief and a slide-in LED frame system. Version 2 improves light sealing, assembly, and orientation accuracy for Northern Hemisphere display.","author":"DazedDice","print_time_ai":"67h (full 50 cm version)","material_ai":"Estimated 800–1200g PLA across 13 plates at €0.025/g","downloads":"2.9k","likes":"","search_volume":"6800","search_trend":"↑ 18% YoY","etsy_listings":"1400","etsy_avg_price":"€74","market_insight":"<b>Celestial and moon-themed wall décor shows sustained growth</b> driven by the ''cottagecore'' and space-aesthetic trends popular with Etsy''s core under-35 female buyer segment. Competition at the 50 cm illuminated level is relatively low — most Etsy moon lamp listings are small tabletop versions under 20 cm, giving this large-format piece a genuine differentiation angle. <b>However, the 67-hour print time is the single biggest production constraint</b> — on one printer a new seller can realistically complete fewer than 2 units per week, capping monthly output severely and making it critical to price high enough to justify each run.","sell_price":"€60.00","units_per_month":"4","gross_revenue":"240","print_cost":"78","etsy_fees":"","net_profit":"162","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optim