(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/sv/models/2349139-plant-trellis-support-dog-theme#profileId-2568968', 'Plant Trellis Support — Dog Theme', 52, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€250/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:36:45.466Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/sv/models/2349139-plant-trellis-support-dog-theme#profileId-2568968","source_host":"makerworld.com/sv/models/2349139-plant-trellis-support-dog-theme","score":"52","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Plant Trellis Support — Dog Theme","description":"A decorative dog-shaped plant stake designed to support soft-stemmed houseplants like Pothos, Maranta, and Philodendron while adding a cute silhouette to the pot. Prints in under an hour with no supports required.","author":"Balrog","print_time_ai":"57 min","material_ai":"~20g PLA","downloads":"","likes":"","search_volume":"9400","search_trend":"↑ 12% YoY","etsy_listings":"4800","etsy_avg_price":"€22","market_insight":"<b>Demand is real but fragmented:</b> plant-lover gifting is one of Etsy''s strongest hobby niches, peaking sharply in November–December and around Mother''s Day, but the ''plant stake'' sub-category sits in a crowded mid-tier where buyers expect either personalisation or striking visual design to justify paying above €8–10. <b>The dog silhouette adds differentiation</b> over plain wire stakes, but competing 3D-printed animal plant stakes already exist on Etsy in volume — a new seller from Sweden shipping worldwide will face both listing-ranking disadvantage and shipping-cost pressure against US-based competitors. <b>Production is not the bottleneck</b> — at 57 minutes per unit a single FDM printer can output 10–12 units per day — but converting traffic without reviews is the real constraint for a new seller.","sell_price":"€22.00","units_per_month":"18","gross_revenue":"396","print_cost":"13","etsy_fees":"40","net_profit":"250","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but ha