(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/en/models/564191-optimized-sd-micro-sd-card-holder-travel-box?from=search#profileId-483811', 'Optimized SD / micro SD Card Holder Travel Box', 58, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€1132/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-04-29T09:00:37.511Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/en/models/564191-optimized-sd-micro-sd-card-holder-travel-box?from=search#profileId-483811","source_host":"makerworld.com/en/models/564191-optimized-sd-micro-sd-card-holder-travel-box","score":"58","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Optimized SD / micro SD Card Holder Travel Box","description":"A compact screw-lid box holding 5 SD cards and 6 micro SD cards, designed to be rugged, pocket-sized, and optionally watertight depending on print material. Optimised for minimal footprint while remaining durable enough for travel use.","author":"BorgoTechSpace","print_time_ai":"2.2h","material_ai":"~35g PLA","downloads":"5.1k","likes":"","search_volume":"1800","search_trend":"→ Stable","etsy_listings":"320","etsy_avg_price":"€14","market_insight":"<b>Competition from mass-manufactured alternatives is the core challenge</b> — injection-moulded SD card cases sell for €3–8 on Amazon and AliExpress, creating a steep price-justification hurdle for a 3D-printed version at €15–30. Etsy listings in this category are sparse (~320), suggesting low competition but also low buyer demand specifically on Etsy. <b>Seasonality is mild</b> — slight uptick around photography-heavy seasons (summer travel, Christmas gifting) but no strong spike. Buyer perception of 3D-printed functional storage items is neutral-to-positive only when a clear differentiator exists, such as custom engraving, a personalised name, or a colour-matched set — without that, the 3D-printed origin reads as ''DIY'' rather than ''premium'' to the average Etsy shopper.","sell_price":"€22.00","units_per_month":"60","gross_revenue":"1320","print_cos