(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/en/models/2533931-bubble-letters-wall-art?from=search#profileId-2788953', 'Bubble Letters Wall Art', 72, 'Good for the right audience', NULL, '~€255/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-05-05T03:14:24.679Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/en/models/2533931-bubble-letters-wall-art?from=search#profileId-2788953","source_host":"makerworld.com/en/models/2533931-bubble-letters-wall-art","score":"72","verdict":"Good for the right audience","title":"Bubble Letters Wall Art","description":"A full-alphabet set of chunky, glossy-finish bubble letters designed for nursery and kids room wall decor, inspired by expensive ceramic boutique lettering. Lightweight, safe to mount, and fully resizable for personalised name displays.","author":"Ace''s Designs","print_time_ai":"19.1h (full plate set)","material_ai":"Estimated 180–300g PLA per full plate set (scale per letters needed)","downloads":"","likes":"","search_volume":"9400","search_trend":"↑ 18% YoY","etsy_listings":"14000","etsy_avg_price":"€22","market_insight":"<b>Demand is strong and evergreen</b> — nursery personalisation is one of the most resilient Etsy gift categories with consistent year-round search volume peaking Nov–Dec and around baby shower season (Mar–May). <b>Competition is high at 14,000+ listings</b>, but the majority are laser-cut wood or printed paper — 3D printed ceramic-look bubble letters with a painted finish occupy a distinct premium niche within that crowd. <b>Buyer perception is positive</b> when the finish is high quality — the painted, sanded, glossy result this design targets looks artisan rather than plastic, which is exactly what Etsy buyers expect at this price point.","sell_price":"€24.00","units_per_month":"18","gross_revenue":"432","print_cost":"121","etsy_fees":"56","net_profit":"255","manufacturing_verdict":"Ideal method","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":"Personalisation — buyers pay a consistent 2–3x premium for a custom name or initials set, and 3D printing is the only method that makes one-off per-name production economically viable at this volume.","etsy_ban_risk":"medium","etsy_ban_reason":"The scraped description references a Patreon for commercial use questions, which implies a separate commercial licence is required beyond the free download — the exact licence terms are not explicitly stated in the scraped data, so the seller must check the model page licence tab and message Ace''s Designs directly via Patreon or MakerWorld to obtain a confirmed print-for-sale licence before listing on Etsy.","legal_risk":"medium","legal_desc":"Because this product targets worldwide buyers including the US, CPSC/CPSIA applies for any item marketed for children under 12 — plastic letters used in a nursery or kids room may be classified as a childrens product requiring ASTM F963-23 testing and a Children''s Product Certificate; the seller should seek legal advice on whether decorative wall-mount letters fall under this classification before scaling.","copyright_risk":"low","copyright_desc":"The bubble letter forms are generic typographic shapes with no identifiable third-party IP holder — the design originates with Ace''s Designs on MakerWorld and contains no licensed characters, logos, or brand marks","best_platform":"","category":"decor","marketplace":"","price_range":"","print_time_input":"","material_input":"","seller_goal":"business","printer_count":"","printer_type":"","experience":"","weekly_time":"","active_markets":"","social_media":"","sell_from":"","sell_to":"WORLDWIDE","legal_flags":""}}'::jsonb, NULL, '2026-05-05T03:14:24.679Z'),
(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/fr/models/623494-easy-clean-toothbrush-holder-with-replacable-tray?from=recommend#profileId-547720', 'Easy Clean Toothbrush Holder with Replaceable Tray', 52, 'Marginal — needs a unique angle', NULL, '~€271/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-05-05T08:53:54.465Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/fr/models/623494-easy-clean-toothbrush-holder-with-replacable-tray?from=recommend#profileId-547720","source_host":"makerworld.com/fr/models/623494","score":"52","verdict":"Marginal — needs a unique angle","title":"Easy Clean Toothbrush Holder with Replaceable Tray","description":"A modular toothbrush holder featuring a removable grate and tray for easy cleaning, designed as a multi-part snap-together assembly. Printed across 5 plates in approximately 7.4 hours, it targets bathroom organisation buyers looking for a hygienic alternative to standard cup holders.","author":"pearigee","print_time_ai":"7.4h","material_ai":"~120g PLA (estimated for 5-plate multi-part assembly at €0.025/g)","downloads":"6.2k","likes":"","search_volume":"9400","search_trend":"→ Stable","etsy_listings":"4200","etsy_avg_price":"€22","market_insight":"<b>Demand exists but competition is high</b> — bathroom organisers are a saturated Etsy category with thousands of ceramic, bamboo, and injection-moulded listings that buyers perceive as more premium than FDM plastic. <b>3D-printed versions can compete on the functional/modular angle</b> (the removable tray is a genuine differentiator), but without personalisation or a distinctive finish, most buyers will default to a cheaper Amazon alternative priced at €8–15. <b>Seasonality is mild</b> — small bathroom accessories see modest gift peaks in November–December but are not strongly seasonal, limiting flash-sale upside for a testing-phase seller.","sell_price":"€22.00","units_per_month":"18","gross_revenue":"396","print_cost":"81","etsy_fees":"44","net_profit":"271","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":"Zero tooling — the multi-part snap-fit design with a replaceable tray grate is testable at €0 upfront and would cost thousands in injection-mould tooling to replicate commercially.","etsy_ban_risk":"medium","etsy_ban_reason":"The MakerWorld listing does not display an explicit commercial or print-for-sale license in the scraped data — you should open the model page, check the license tab, and if no commercial license is stated, message pearigee directly to request written permission before listing prints for sale on Etsy.","legal_risk":"medium","legal_desc":"As an EU seller based in France shipping worldwide, you are subject to the EU General Product Safety Regulation (GPSR, in force December 2024), which requires a Declaration of Conformity, an EU Responsible Person designation, and a GPSR compliance statement on your Etsy shop; shipping to the USA does not trigger CPSC requirements for this non-toy adult bathroom item, but California Prop 65 warnings are advisable if using standard PLA with dyes.","copyright_risk":"low","copyright_desc":"The design is an original functional utility","best_platform":"","category":"decor","marketplace":"etsy","price_range":"15-30","print_time_input":"","material_input":"","seller_goal":"testing","printer_count":"","printer_type":"","experience":"some","weekly_time":"","active_markets":"","social_media":"","sell_from":"FR","sell_to":"WORLDWIDE","legal_flags":"none"}}'::jsonb, NULL, '2026-05-05T08:53:54.465Z');
