(NULL, 'https://makerworld.com/it/models/610818-skadis-tool-holders?from=search#profileId-533951', 'Skadis Tool Holders', 32, 'Don''t sell — license blocks commercial use', NULL, '~€853/mo', FALSE, FALSE, '{"source":"google-sheets-import","original":{"timestamp":"2026-05-05T09:20:37.818Z","input_url":"https://makerworld.com/it/models/610818-skadis-tool-holders?from=search#profileId-533951","source_host":"makerworld.com/it/models/610818-skadis-tool-holders","score":"32","verdict":"Don''t sell — license blocks commercial use","title":"Skadis Tool Holders","description":"A set of 3D-printed tool holders designed for the IKEA Skadis pegboard system, including holders for a printhead, scraper, glue, pliers, and various 3D printer maintenance accessories. The set spans 5 print plates and requires T-clips for mounting.","author":"kactum","print_time_ai":"15.5h","material_ai":"~180g PLA (estimated across 5 plates)","downloads":"8.4k","likes":"","search_volume":"3200","search_trend":"→ Stable","etsy_listings":"1800","etsy_avg_price":"€14","market_insight":"<b>Demand for Skadis accessories on Etsy is real but shallow</b> — search volume is moderate and the category is dominated by cheap injection-moulded IKEA originals and AliExpress alternatives that undercut 3D-printed versions on price. <b>This specific set is hyper-targeted at 3D printer owners</b>, an audience that almost certainly already owns a printer and would simply download and print the file themselves rather than buy it — dramatically shrinking the addressable buyer pool. At a target price of €60+, the product is <b>far above the verified Etsy price ceiling of ~€25 for functional pegboard organisers</b>, making conversion extremely unlikely without a strong personalisation or premium-branding angle.","sell_price":"€60.00","units_per_month":"18","gross_revenue":"1080","print_cost":"119","etsy_fees":"108","net_profit":"853","manufacturing_verdict":"Works, but has limits","is_3d_optimal":"TRUE","printing_advantage":