","printing_advantage":"Geometry — the single-wall vase-mode construction creates a semi-translucent light-diffusing shell that no other low-cost manufacturing method can reproduce at this price point.","etsy_ban_risk":"medium","etsy_ban_reason":"No explicit commercial or print-for-sale license is visible in the scraped data for this MakerWorld model — the seller should check the license tab on the model page and, if no commercial license is stated, message the designer Tom directly to request written permission before listing prints for sale on Etsy.","legal_risk":"high","legal_desc":"Because this product incorporates an electrical LED component and is sold worldwide (including the EU, UK, and USA), it triggers multiple frameworks: EU GPSR (Dec 2024) requires a Declaration of Conformity and EU Responsible Person; LVD (2014/35/EU) and EMC (2014/30/EU) directives apply to the assembled lamp; in the USA, FCC Part 15 and UL 153 (portable lamps) are relevant; in the UK, UKCA replaces CE. The seller must either sell the printed parts only","copyright_risk":"","copyright_desc":"","best_platform":"","category":"decor","marketplace":"etsy","price_range":"15-30","print_time_input":"","material_input":"","seller_goal":"side-hustle","printer_count":"","printer_type":"","experience":"some","weekly_time":"","active_markets":"","social_media":"","sell_from":"","sell_to":"WORLDWIDE","legal_flags":""}}'::jsonb, NULL, '2026-05-05T17:12:02.710Z'),
